quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  37,1,Mi woondirii saffiniraa…ói …óin saffaaji
  37,2,Mi woondirii soggiray…ói (duule) …óin soggugol
  37,3,"Mi woondirii janngiray…ói …óin, anndintinorgol"
  37,4,"Pellet, rewetee…óo mon On, ko bajjo"
  37,5,"Jey…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, e kon ko woni hakkunde …óin …ói…ói, Jey…óo kadi fu…óir…óe …óen"
  37,6,"Men cu…óirii kammu (hikkii ngu) aduna ngun: cu…óaari koode …óen"
  37,7,e reenirgol (ngu) kala seytaane ra…óaandu
  37,8,"∆äi ha…ótanaaka he…óitagol mbatu [Malaa'ika'en] toowu ngu ngun; tawde hi…ói feroree e kala baŇčŇče"
  37,9,"ka ra…óagol (…ói). Hino woodani …ói kadi, lepte duumii…óe"
  37,10,"Si wanaa ndun bifti ndu e majji, jilannde [haala], ndu rewniree hoodere tufaynde"
  37,11,"Lamndo …ďe: si ko kam…ďe …ďuri sa…ótude tagude kaa ko …ďen …ďe Men tagi? Men tagirii …ďe kam…ďe, loopal narnungal"
  37,12,"Si ko woni, a haawi, hi…ďe jalnora"
  37,13,"Si …ďe waajaama, …ďe waajitortaa"
  37,14,"si …ďe yi'ii maande, …ďe jalkita"
  37,15,"…ďe wi'a: \"∆äum wonaali, si wanaa mbilewu …ďanngu ngu"
  37,16,"Eyoo si men maayii, men wontii mbullaari e ∆īi'e, haray ko men immintinoytee…ďe"
  37,17,Baabiraa…ďe amen adinoo…ďe …ďen kadi e minen
  37,18,"Maaku: \"Pellet! Hara le ko on hoynaa…ďe"
  37,19,"Anndon …óum, ko wuttaandu wooturu pet, tawee jaka yoo, hi…ďe ndaara"
  37,20,"∆Āe wi'a: Ee bone amen ! Ko ndee woni √Ďalaande njo…ďdi kuu…óe"
  37,21,"Ko ndee woni √Ďalaande √Īaawoore, ko fennayno…óon fii mun"
  37,22,"Moo…ďee too√Īu…ďe …ďen, e nandadii…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, e kon ko …ďe wonunoo e rewde"
  37,23,ko wonaa Alla. Soggiree…ďe ka laawol Jahiimi
  37,24,"Darnon …ďe, tawde ko …ďe lamnditetee…ďe"
